projects.name: Software Development
projects.description:
Library Management System,
A centralized platform for library staff to efficiently manage library resources and provide seamless services to customer. The system supports functionalities such as adding, editing, and deleting books from the inventory, managing customer information, facilitating borrowing, and returning of book copies, generating reports, and more. It aims to enhance the overall efficiency and effectiveness of library operations developed using Java.
Includes Requirements Analysis, Use Case diagram, TDD with JUnit5 and EasyMock guarantees reliability and accuracy of the system.
